title: The View from Stanford Court Hotel
long_description:
It’s no secret that at Stanford Court Hotel, we love art. We also love to see #SF through our guest’s lens on Instagram.  

Here are our favorite Insta photos by our awesome guests @StanfordCourtSF. Keep sharing!

Check out the view from our hotel window looking out at the beautiful Grace Cathedral. The brownstone in the foreground is the Pacific-Union Club. This view is from one of our guests looking out on California Street.

Photo credit @breegotacamera

Have you tried the deliciously rich, organic coffee from Equator? It’s just as serious as this pup’s expression. Available at SCH and surrounding areas. Go ahead, have a cup.

Photo credit @korystev

We love this fall foliage shot of the SCH exterior. Check out that incline!

Photo credit @happyisprettyblog

Did you know we have free bike rentals at #SCH? We are big fans of this photo taken by one of our guests. Interested? Check out our recommended bike rides here. 

Photo credit @Patricejustin

We are big fans of this photo overlooking #SF. Gorgeous views from all angles at #SCH

Photo credit @zubbymom7

Visiting #SCH? We’d love to see your photos. Tag us at @StanfordCourtSF so we can see SF through your lens.
